# Charles Schwab uses a standard OAuth 2.0 Authorization Code Grant flow.
# The full sequence (one-time setup per refresh token):
#
#   STEP 1: User enters App Key + Secret in the dashboard and clicks "Save Keys"
#   STEP 2: User clicks "Generate Auth Link" -- Schwab login page opens in browser
#   STEP 3: User logs into Schwab and clicks "Approve" to authorize the app
#   STEP 4: Schwab redirects the browser to: https://127.0.0.1/?code=XXXX...
#   STEP 5: User copies that full URL and pastes it into the dashboard
#   STEP 6: We POST the code to /token and receive access_token + refresh_token
#   STEP 7: Every 30 min the access_token is auto-refreshed using refresh_token
#
# SECURITY: Real credentials go in schwab_tokens.json (gitignored).
